{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.length","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage/length","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><em><code>length</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>removeItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>setItem()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Storage API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>A propriedade length, que é somente leitura, da interface&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a>&nbsp;retorna um inteiro que representa o número de itens armazenados no objeto&nbsp;<code>Storage</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>aLength</em> = <em>storage</em>.length;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"retorno","title":"Retorno","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um inteiro</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A função a seguir adiciona três itens ('bgcolor', 'font' e 'image') ao local storage do domínio atual, em seguida&nbsp;retorna o número de itens no storage:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'yellow'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Helvetica'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'cats.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// should return 3</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Nota</strong>: Para um exemplo do mundo real, veja nosso&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/web-storage-demo\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage Demo</a>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"about:unknown#dom-storage-length\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'length' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-\">Desconhecido</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>localStorage</td>\n   <td>4</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>3.5</td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td>10.50</td>\n   <td>4</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>sessionStorage</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>2</td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td>10.50</td>\n   <td>4</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>2.1</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td>11</td>\n   <td>iOS 3.2</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>Cada browser tem uma capacidade variada para&nbsp;localStorage e&nbsp;sessionStorage. Aqui existe um&nbsp;<a class=\"external\" href=\"http://dev-test.nemikor.com/web-storage/support-test/\" rel=\" noopener\">tabela detalhada sobre a capacidade de armazenamento de cada browser</a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect4\">\n<p><strong>Nota: </strong>desde o iOS 5.1, o Safari Mobile armazena os dados do&nbsp;localStorage no folder de&nbsp;cache, que está sujeito a uma limpeza ocasional baseada em regras do SO, tipicamente, quando o espaço está se esgotando.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\">Usando a API&nbsp;Web Storage</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A propriedade length, que é somente leitura, da interface Storage retorna um inteiro que representa o número de itens armazenados no objeto Storage.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/storage/length","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/storage/length/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage","title":"Storage"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Storage/length","title":"Storage.length"}],"pageTitle":"Storage.length - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}